22:39.944 --> 22:44.909
doing sales engineering on mechanical power 
transmission equipment. What was the money you

22:45.009 --> 22:46.551
made from those? Chains. Both V-belts, 
couplings, bearings, belts. I mentioned

22:55.183 --> 22:56.386
V-belts. You were selling these to Cummings. Yes. 
It was a sale. And more often than not, you had to go

23:00.676 --> 23:10.411
out and tell a man what he needed because he was 
there ready to buy, but he didn't know what he

23:00.676 --> 23:10.411
needed to buy. He didn't really know what he needed 
to buy, so you had an engineering project right

