23:17.381 --> 23:27.156
the correct merchandise, and then you gradually 
build up on it. And you went to Dix County from 38 to

23:29.279 --> 23:33.986
41? No, I was from 37, I'd say. I guess about 37 there 
until about 39. Then what? I came back here and they

23:51.385 --> 23:56.010
got me to working part-time on A&M. I came back here 
and my father-in-law, who was an attorney,

23:56.651 --> 24:08.845
I married in 1935.

24:09.326 --> 24:14.912
I was working in Port Arthur, but I came up here to 
marry. My father-in-law was an attorney. He was an

24:17.855 --> 24:22.199
attorney here, and he was an attorney and a 
